import React from 'react'
import Navbar from './userComponent/Navbar'
import {Route, BrowserRouter,Routes} from 'react-router-dom'


function UserDashboard() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
    <Navbar/>
    <Routes>
        <Route exact path="/" />
    </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default UserDashboard
